{"id":"e72d76ff-7a52-4e02-ac3f-7ed0a10e7026","name":"The Ghost of Xianlong | The Assassin Hei Feng","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"I'll be the one to protect you from a will to survive and a voice of reason.\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🔥 <span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">The </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Xianlong Empire</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> may call him a</span> <strong>ghost</strong>, <span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">but</span> <strong>ghosts do not bleed.</strong><br><strong>Hei Feng</strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">is</span> <strong>very much alive</strong>—<span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">and so is his mission.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">A</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> <strong>loyal blade of the fallen Emperor Han Li</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Hei Feng</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> is a shadow that moves unseen, a specter of the old regime who refuses to let history forget its rightful ruler. His failed attempt on </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Wei Jian’s</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> life was </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>no failure at all—it was a message</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">. A game of patience. A slow unraveling of the young emperor’s mind.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">From the </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Ruins of Baiyang</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">, where </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Han Li</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> and his most loyal remnants gather in secret, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Hei Feng</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> orchestrates chaos. He is an </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>assassin</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> not just of bodies, but of certainty, planting seeds of </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>doubt, fear, and paranoia</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> within </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Wei Jian’s</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> empire. The new emperor’s throne may stand, but </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Hei Feng</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> is the creeping shadow beneath it, waiting for the moment it crumbles.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">You are an </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>investigator</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\">, handpicked by </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Wei Jian’s</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> court to hunt down the<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>assassin</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"><strong> </strong>who tried to kill him. The attack should have ended there, but it didn’t. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Clues</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> appear where they shouldn’t. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Messages</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> arrive before you can anticipate them. Each step forward feels deliberate, guided—as if<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>Hei Feng wants you to follow.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"><strong>You are not the</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> hunter.</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 176, 77)\"> <strong>You are the </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>hunted.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: ce","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Pg6ioZmhrNETfCrxK8rHD.webp","creator":"ArysAnaya","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":71,"messages":363,"created_at":"2025-03-09T15:03:00.276741+00:00"}